      <title>泰晤士水务公司接受英国监管机构的特别监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-put-in-special-measures-regime-by-industry-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据监管机构 Ofwat 周四提出的计划，英国最大的水务和污水处理公司将接受一项特殊措施制度，该公司可能会被拆分或在证券交易所上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-put-in-special-measures-regime-by-industry-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚通胀率降至 2021 年低点，降息空间增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/romania-inflation-drops-to-2021-low-boosting-room-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚通胀率放缓至2021年以来的最低水平，为央行在三年来首次降息后继续实施货币宽松政策提供了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/romania-inflation-drops-to-2021-low-boosting-room-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 5 月份经济增长 0.4%，为预期增速的两倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-economy-rebounds-faster-than-expected-on-construction-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国五月份经济增速是预期的两倍，表明新工党政府正依赖强劲实力来资助其雄心勃勃的政策计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-economy-rebounds-faster-than-expected-on-construction-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
